&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be part of a dynamic Finance team that values good vibes, teamwork, and efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take ownership of core financial processes while working with cutting-edge tools and AI solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gain exposure to global operations and cross-functional collaboration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead cross-functional and multi-entity process improvements and automations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Record invoices, payments, and GL transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead key aspects of the monthly closing process, including provisions, prepaid expenses&amp;nbsp; and allocation expenses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and submit VAT reports, withholding tax and other tax reportings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities for process improvement and automation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain Fixed Asset records.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage day-to-day bookkeeping and accounting activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
