&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make a direct impact by shaping how we define and measure success across the GTM organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with smart, passionate teams in a data-centric and supportive environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll be:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
