&lt;li&gt;Build reports, dashboards, and metrics to deliver actionable insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as an analytics focal point, working closely with a wide range of cross-functional teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
