&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in SQL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and cross-functional collaboration skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High level of independence and self-motivation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to thrive in a fast-paced, dynamic environment and manage multiple priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 2+ years of experience as a Business/Data Analyst or similar role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BA/BSc in Industrial Engineering, Information Systems, Economics, Statistics, Mathematics, or a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Salesforce&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in modeling data tables and building scalable data models&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
