&lt;li&gt;Freedom to innovate and implement impactful solutions that directly enhance Yotpo’s overall security posture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage with a wide range of projects to develop deep knowledge across multiple security domains.&lt;/li&gt;
