&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least 3 years of experience managing and leading engineering teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least 3 years of hands-on experience working with React in production environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong experience in frontend architecture and building scalable systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience working cross-functionally with multiple stakeholders across engineering and product teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills and the ability to influence technical direction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
