&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hands-On Technical Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; This is a highly active role. You aren&#39;t just managing from a distance; you will write code, build prototypes, review PRs, and work side-by-side with your engineers to design scalable systems (LLM pipelines, data ingestion, and event-driven architectures).&lt;/li&gt;
