&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cultivate an AI-Native Engineering Culture:&lt;/strong&gt; Champion modern developer experiences (DevEx) within the team. Drive the adoption of agentic workflows and automated internal tools to eliminate boilerplate and amplify the team&#39;s delivery velocity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
