&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Hands-On, Battle-Tested Leader:&lt;/strong&gt; 5+ years of experience leading engineering teams within fast-paced startup environments and rapidly changing landscapes. You are passionate about coaching developers directly and keeping your own coding and architecture skills sharp.&lt;/li&gt;
