&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Must Haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6+ years of experience building scalable backend services in a production environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Backend Fluency:&lt;/strong&gt; Strong proficiency in modern backend languages (&lt;strong&gt;Java, Python, or Node.js&lt;/strong&gt;) and their ecosystems.&lt;/li&gt;
